---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-github-border/50 bg-github-bg/50 backdrop-blur-xl">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-primary to-brand-secondary rounded-lg
                      flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">
            GB
          </div>
          <span class="text-white font-display font-bold">GitHubBook</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-github-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          每日追踪 GitHub Trending，深度解读 AI 与开源项目趋势。
          帮助开发者发现下一个改变世界的项目。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">快速导航</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/githubbook/" class="text-github-muted hover:text-brand-primary text-sm transition-colors">首页</a></li>
          <li><a href="/githubbook/trending/" class="text-github-muted hover:text-brand-primary text-sm transition-colors">GitHub热点</a></li>
          <li><a href="/githubbook/ai-school/" class="text-github-muted hover:text-brand-primary text-sm transition-colors">AI学堂</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Subscribe / Info -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3">关于本站</h4>
        <p class="text-github-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">
          每日自动抓取 GitHub Trending 数据，AI 辅助生成深度分析博文。
          内容每日更新，欢迎收藏关注。
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <a href="https://github.com/allli0379/githubbook" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="text-github-muted hover:text-white transition-colors"
             aria-label="GitHub Repository">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <span class="text-github-muted text-xs">Powered by Astro & GitHub Actions</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-github-border/30 text-center text-github-muted text-xs">
      &copy; {currentYear} GitHubBook. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
